activities:
BitTitan uses personal information to:  •	Provide, maintain and improve the BitTitan Service Offerings, process transactions and send you related information, including confirmations, invoices, technical notices, updates, security alerts and support and administrative messages;
•	Respond to your comments, questions and requests and provide customer service;
•	Communicate with you about products, services, offers, promotions, rewards, and events offered by BitTitan and others, and provide news and information we think will be of interest to you;
•	Monitor and analyze trends, usage and activities in connection with the BitTitan Service Offerings;
•	Automatically determine if you are using the most current version of our software and/or third party software and notify you if an upgrade is available;
•	Personalize and improve the BitTitan Service Offerings and provide advertisements, content or features that match user profiles or interests;
•	Link or combine with information we get from others to help understand your needs and provide you with better service; and
•	Carry out any other purpose for which the information was collected.
